149
00:09:14,564 --> 00:09:17,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eight-Six and R32 going at it on the downhill!</b></font>

150
00:09:17,804 --> 00:09:21,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Eight-Six? That's news to me!</b></font>

151
00:09:21,204 --> 00:09:26,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! The word is, Nakazato came
to this gas station in person</b></font>

152
00:09:26,204 --> 00:09:28,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>to issue the challenge!</b></font>

153
00:09:28,874 --> 00:09:31,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi. Have you heard anything about this?</b></font>

154
00:09:31,544 --> 00:09:33,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, not a word.</b></font>

155
00:09:33,344 --> 00:09:36,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No one knows about this? What's going on?</b></font>

156
00:09:36,884 --> 00:09:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>S-Sorry!</b></font>

157
00:09:41,024 --> 00:09:44,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki... you didn't...</b></font>

158
00:09:44,494 --> 00:09:48,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I... I accepted the challenge!</b></font>

159
00:09:50,534 --> 00:09:52,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please forgive me!</b></font>

160
00:09:52,534 --> 00:09:56,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yesterday, Nakazato of the
Night Kids really came here.</b></font>

161
00:09:56,674 --> 00:10:01,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He came by when Iketani
and Takumi were out. I...</b></font>

162
00:10:01,514 --> 00:10:04,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I couldn't help but pretend to be
a member of the Speed Stars...</b></font>

163
00:10:04,344 --> 00:10:06,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and before I knew what was happening...</b></font>

164
00:10:06,744 --> 00:10:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...he had already issued
the challenge and driven off.</b></font>

165
00:10:09,614 --> 00:10:13,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why didn't you tell us about this before?!</b></font>

166
00:10:13,524 --> 00:10:18,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was going to tell you, I swear.
I was just waiting for the right moment.</b></font>

167
00:10:18,124 --> 00:10:21,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi, I'm sorry. I messed up.</b></font>

168
00:10:21,564 --> 00:10:24,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Please forgive me!</b></font>

169
00:10:24,364 --> 00:10:26,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a bit late now...</b></font>

170
00:10:26,564 --> 00:10:31,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Forgive me... Please forgive me...</b></font>

171
00:10:37,614 --> 00:10:40,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Looks like the R32's out again tonight.</b></font>

172
00:10:40,044 --> 00:10:43,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's racing against the
Eight-Six tomorrow night, right?</b></font>

173
00:10:43,714 --> 00:10:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm definitely going to watch that!</b></font>

174
00:10:46,384 --> 00:10:49,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If Nakazato of the Night Kids
is challenging the Eight-Six</b></font>

175
00:10:49,124 --> 00:10:51,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that beat Keisuke Takahashi,</b></font>

176
00:10:51,464 --> 00:10:54,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>there's no way we can miss that!</b></font>

177
00:10:54,094 --> 00:10:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On the surface it may seem like a race</b></font>

178
00:10:56,064 --> 00:10:58,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>between the Speed Stars and the Night Kids,</b></font>

179
00:10:58,464 --> 00:11:01,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but it's really a battle
between Nakazato's pride</b></font>

180
00:11:01,174 --> 00:11:03,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the pride of the Red Suns'
Takahashi Brothers!</b></font>

181
00:11:03,874 --> 00:11:05,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No matter how the race turns out,</b></font>

182
00:11:05,944 --> 00:11:08,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ryosuke Takahashi's not going
to just sit back and watch.</b></font>

183
00:11:08,774 --> 00:11:12,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The summer nights are
starting to heat up already!</b></font>

184
00:11:15,414 --> 00:11:18,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, man...</b></font>

185
00:11:20,424 --> 00:11:22,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What are we going to do?</b></font>

186
00:11:22,354 --> 00:11:24,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Everyone around town's
talking about this race.</b></font>

187
00:11:24,594 --> 00:11:26,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's too late to back out now.</b></font>

188
00:11:26,864 --> 00:11:30,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe I'd better ask Takumi to race.</b></font>

189
00:11:30,394 --> 00:11:35,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even Takumi might not have
what it takes to go against the R32.</b></font>

190
00:11:35,434 --> 00:11:41,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That Night Kid Nakazato is as famous
a racer as the Takahashi Brothers...</b></font>

191
00:11:41,314 --> 00:11:46,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be a tough battle. It might
even be over from the get-go.</b></font>

192
00:11:46,784 --> 00:11:52,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>On second thought, maybe I
shouldn't ask him after all.</b></font>

193
00:12:10,204 --> 00:12:13,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There you go.</b></font>

194
00:12:13,074 --> 00:12:15,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey... Dad.</b></font>

195
00:12:15,744 --> 00:12:17,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is an R32 any good?</b></font>

196
00:12:17,374 --> 00:12:21,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>R32? Yeah... That's a fast car...</b></font>

197
00:12:21,684 --> 00:12:24,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could you win? In a downhill...</b></font>

198
00:12:24,384 --> 00:12:27,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...against the R32?</b></font>

199
00:12:27,354 --> 00:12:32,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah. I'd win against any
car I raced, R32 or not.</b></font>

200
00:12:34,534 --> 00:12:37,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you think... I can win?</b></font>

201
00:12:37,264 --> 00:12:39,304
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't know...</b></font>

202
00:12:39,304 --> 00:12:43,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It'd be a close race.</b></font>

203
00:12:43,204 --> 00:12:45,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why are you asking?</b></font>

204
00:12:45,744 --> 00:12:47,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You gonna race an R32?</b></font>

205
00:12:47,944 --> 00:12:48,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No...</b></font>

206
00:12:48,974 --> 00:12:52,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm... I'm just asking...</b></font>

207
00:12:52,784 --> 00:12:54,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>See ya.</b></font>

208
00:12:54,784 --> 00:12:58,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

209
00:13:04,024 --> 00:13:06,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Now it's against an R32...</i></b></font>

210
00:13:06,564 --> 00:13:10,264
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'd better adjust the Eight-Six's settings...</i></b></font>

211
00:13:17,004 --> 00:13:21,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>It'd be a close race.</i></b></font>

212
00:13:56,874 --> 00:14:00,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I thought I'd find you if I
came here around this time.</b></font>

213
00:14:00,614 --> 00:14:04,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It was about this time the night I first met you.</b></font>

214
00:14:04,324 --> 00:14:07,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you're going against Nakazato
from the Night Kids, huh?</b></font>

215
00:14:07,824 --> 00:14:11,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the talk of the town.</b></font>

216
00:14:11,564 --> 00:14:15,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For your information, I don't
recall accepting that challenge.</b></font>

217
00:14:15,394 --> 00:14:17,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?!</b></font>

218
00:14:17,234 --> 00:14:20,664
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He came to challenge me while I was away.</b></font>

219
00:14:20,664 --> 00:14:22,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't intend to race him.</b></font>

220
00:14:22,574 --> 00:14:24,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What do you mean you
don't intend to race him?</b></font>

221
00:14:26,874 --> 00:14:31,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Night Kid Nakazato issued a
personal challenge to you, right?</b></font>

222
00:14:31,344 --> 00:14:33,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why don't you just accept it?</b></font>

223
00:14:33,544 --> 00:14:38,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Show him who's the fastest! You can beat him!</b></font>

224
00:14:38,024 --> 00:14:42,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why does it matter to you?
This is between him and me.</b></font>

225
00:14:42,424 --> 00:14:44,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, it's not just between you two!</b></font>

226
00:14:44,394 --> 00:14:48,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's because you beat me!</b></font>

227
00:14:48,294 --> 00:14:53,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you lose to anyone, it's gotta
be to the Takahashi Brothers!</b></font>

228
00:14:53,634 --> 00:14:55,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Until one of us beats you,
you can't lose to anyone else!</b></font>

229
00:14:55,974 --> 00:14:58,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Not even to the R32!</b></font>

230
00:14:58,544 --> 00:15:02,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I said I wasn't going to race him!
I have no reason to.</b></font>

231
00:15:02,544 --> 00:15:08,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Reason? Does any racer need a reason to race?</b></font>

232
00:15:08,414 --> 00:15:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who ever said I was a racer?</b></font>

233
00:15:11,424 --> 00:15:16,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm in no mood for jokes!
Are you being sarcastic?!</b></font>

234
00:15:16,524 --> 00:15:18,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>In order for your technique
to be as good as it is,</b></font>

235
00:15:18,764 --> 00:15:21,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>you must have practiced for years!</b></font>

236
00:15:21,064 --> 00:15:24,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why would someone drive
like a racer if he's not a racer?!</b></font>

237
00:15:24,734 --> 00:15:27,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I don't drive like I do because I like it.</b></font>

238
00:15:27,004 --> 00:15:30,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I have to in order to help out at home.</b></font>

239
00:15:30,874 --> 00:15:32,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Stop denying it.</b></font>

240
00:15:32,404 --> 00:15:35,774
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No one can get as good
as you if they hate driving.</b></font>

241
00:15:35,774 --> 00:15:39,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's not it... You wouldn't understand.</b></font>

242
00:15:39,514 --> 00:15:42,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're the one who doesn't understand!</b></font>

243
00:15:42,414 --> 00:15:46,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Could someone who hates
racing ever master drifting?</b></font>

244
00:15:46,384 --> 00:15:50,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Only a person who loves the sport
could master something like that!</b></font>

245
00:15:50,394 --> 00:15:53,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe you don't realize it, but you're a racer.</b></font>

246
00:15:53,394 --> 00:15:57,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Deep down you love driving! You hear me?!</b></font>

247
00:15:57,764 --> 00:16:02,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you love driving, then that
makes you racer enough!</b></font>

248
00:16:02,004 --> 00:16:06,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And if you're a racer, then you should
be proud of your driving skills!</b></font>

249
00:16:06,874 --> 00:16:11,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Accepting challenges is a racer's pride!</b></font>

250
00:16:11,584 --> 00:16:14,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You make me sick.</b></font>

251
00:16:33,404 --> 00:16:36,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Do I really like driving...</i></b></font>

252
00:16:36,674 --> 00:16:39,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but just don't realize it?</i></b></font>

253
00:16:42,074 --> 00:16:43,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Still...</i></b></font>

254
00:16:43,574 --> 00:16:48,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...being forced to accept every</i>
<i>challenge that comes along...</i></b></font>

255
00:16:48,284 --> 00:16:50,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>That isn't for me!</i></b></font>

256
00:16:51,584 --> 00:16:54,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Itsuki! Where's Takumi?</b></font>

257
00:16:54,394 --> 00:16:56,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's on the late shift today.</b></font>

258
00:16:56,254 --> 00:16:58,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh...</b></font>

259
00:16:58,424 --> 00:17:01,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Iketani...</b></font>

260
00:17:01,294 --> 00:17:06,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm going to go to Mt. Akina
tonight to apologize to Nakazato.</b></font>

261
00:17:06,964 --> 00:17:08,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki...</b></font>

262
00:17:08,574 --> 00:17:11,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll get down on my knees if I
have to and tell him the truth.</b></font>

263
00:17:11,544 --> 00:17:13,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Maybe he'll understand.</b></font>

264
00:17:13,144 --> 00:17:17,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Besides, the Speed Stars had
nothing to do with this...</b></font>

265
00:17:17,474 --> 00:17:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't think we can
convince Takumi to race?</b></font>

266
00:17:21,014 --> 00:17:25,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No. I know him better than anyone,
and he'll never do it...</b></font>

267
00:17:25,384 --> 00:17:29,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He hates being forced into things</b></font>

268
00:17:29,194 --> 00:17:32,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>or having to follow others' orders.</b></font>

269
00:17:32,064 --> 00:17:34,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He looks real mellow,</b></font>

270
00:17:34,224 --> 00:17:37,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but once he says something,
there's no changing his mind...</b></font>

271
00:17:37,594 --> 00:17:42,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Stubborn... just like his father.</i></b></font>

272
00:17:42,334 --> 00:17:46,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He doesn't understand why
racers have to accept challenges.</b></font>

273
00:17:46,344 --> 00:17:49,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The whole system offends him.</b></font>

274
00:17:49,444 --> 00:17:52,914
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When someone tries to force
him to do something, he snaps.</b></font>

275
00:17:52,914 --> 00:17:54,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>One time in eleventh grade, he flipped out</b></font>

276
00:17:54,754 --> 00:17:57,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and beat up a group of
seniors after soccer practice.</b></font>

277
00:17:57,554 --> 00:18:00,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Takumi did that?</b></font>

278
00:18:13,664 --> 00:18:17,334
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss, I finished cleaning up outside.</b></font>

279
00:18:17,334 --> 00:18:19,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks.</b></font>

280
00:18:19,244 --> 00:18:21,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No problem. See you tomorrow, then.</b></font>

281
00:18:21,644 --> 00:18:23,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

282
00:18:23,174 --> 00:18:25,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come and have a seat.</b></font>

283
00:18:25,484 --> 00:18:27,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Okay...</b></font>

284
00:18:29,154 --> 00:18:33,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know, I overheard some talk.</b></font>

285
00:18:33,254 --> 00:18:35,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You're going to race an R32 tonight?</b></font>

286
00:18:35,594 --> 00:18:37,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What? I'm...</b></font>

287
00:18:37,194 --> 00:18:40,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't do it, Takumi. That guy's bad news.</b></font>

288
00:18:40,894 --> 00:18:42,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh... No, I wasn't...</b></font>

289
00:18:42,764 --> 00:18:46,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No, no. I know what you're going to say.</b></font>

290
00:18:46,904 --> 00:18:49,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've known everything from the beginning.</b></font>

291
00:18:49,874 --> 00:18:54,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I know it wasn't your decision to take this race.</b></font>

292
00:18:54,074 --> 00:18:56,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Itsuki was the one who screwed
up and accepted it, right?</b></font>

293
00:18:56,214 --> 00:18:57,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

294
00:18:57,244 --> 00:19:00,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know, you're too nice sometimes.</b></font>

295
00:19:00,284 --> 00:19:03,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You gotta stop bailing your
friends out all the time.</b></font>

296
00:19:03,884 --> 00:19:07,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Trust me. Whatever you do,
don't race that R32.</b></font>

297
00:19:07,224 --> 00:19:09,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's a lot you don't know about cars.</b></font>

298
00:19:09,494 --> 00:19:13,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Do you even know what an R32 can do?</b></font>

299
00:19:13,524 --> 00:19:16,824
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Is an R32 that amazing?</b></font>

300
00:19:19,364 --> 00:19:21,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gotcha! He took the bait...</i></b></font>

301
00:19:21,804 --> 00:19:24,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's beyond amazing.</b></font>

302
00:19:24,174 --> 00:19:26,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That car's in a class by itself!</b></font>

303
00:19:26,344 --> 00:19:28,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Its driving system combines everything good</b></font>

304
00:19:28,214 --> 00:19:31,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>about FR and four-wheel drive.</b></font>

305
00:19:31,044 --> 00:19:34,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a beast!</b></font>

306
00:19:34,314 --> 00:19:37,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>An Eight-Six or GT-R is no match for it.</b></font>

307
00:19:37,084 --> 00:19:39,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If the driver was an amateur,
you'd have a chance,</b></font>

308
00:19:39,354 --> 00:19:42,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but you're up against a famous racer, right?</b></font>

309
00:19:42,224 --> 00:19:44,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dad didn't tell me this.</i></b></font>

310
00:19:44,524 --> 00:19:47,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He said it'd be a close race.</i></b></font>

311
00:19:47,724 --> 00:19:49,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey.</b></font>

312
00:19:49,164 --> 00:19:51,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You with me?</b></font>

313
00:19:51,064 --> 00:19:55,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You just became famous yourself
by beating that team from Akagi.</b></font>

314
00:19:55,834 --> 00:19:58,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You shouldn't ruin your name so fast...</b></font>

315
00:19:58,504 --> 00:20:02,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not wise to go up against someone
you have no chance of defeating.</b></font>

316
00:20:02,274 --> 00:20:04,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You hear me?</b></font>

317
00:20:04,014 --> 00:20:06,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since your opponent's driving an R32,</b></font>

318
00:20:06,214 --> 00:20:08,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>no one would call you
a coward for backing out.</b></font>

319
00:20:09,584 --> 00:20:11,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A coward?!</i></b></font>

320
00:20:14,924 --> 00:20:17,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Boss...</b></font>

321
00:20:17,424 --> 00:20:21,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks for the warning...</b></font>

322
00:20:21,464 --> 00:20:27,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...but I could care less
about my fame as a racer.</b></font>

323
00:20:30,574 --> 00:20:33,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So you aren't going to back down?</b></font>

324
00:20:33,274 --> 00:20:36,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>No.</b></font>

325
00:20:36,044 --> 00:20:38,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hearing about how amazing that car is</b></font>

326
00:20:38,414 --> 00:20:42,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>has only made me want to see it in action.</b></font>

327
00:20:44,784 --> 00:20:49,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not afraid of an R32 or any other car.</b></font>

328
00:20:53,664 --> 00:20:55,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whew!</b></font>

329
00:20:55,834 --> 00:20:59,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's exactly like his father...</b></font>

330
00:21:03,874 --> 00:21:05,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}"Temporarily Closed</b></font>

331
00:21:03,874 --> 00:21:05,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="66"><b>{\an5}Fujiwara Tofu Shop"</b></font>

332
00:21:07,074 --> 00:21:09,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Temporarily closed?</b></font>

333
00:21:09,614 --> 00:21:11,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Dad never said anything about this.</b></font>

334
00:21:11,744 --> 00:21:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How's he going to make
money if the shop's closed?</b></font>

335
00:21:15,854 --> 00:21:18,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no! The car!</b></font>

336
00:21:20,684 --> 00:21:23,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If he went out drinking, I'm really in trouble.</b></font>

337
00:21:23,594 --> 00:21:27,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He won't be back until morning!</b></font>

338
00:21:27,894 --> 00:21:30,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't do anything without a car.</b></font>

339
00:21:30,434 --> 00:21:33,804
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I should have asked to borrow it this morning!</b></font>

340
00:21:35,604 --> 00:21:37,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Look at the crowd!</b></font>

341
00:21:37,874 --> 00:21:41,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There's even more people out
tonight than at the Akagi race!</b></font>

342
00:21:41,574 --> 00:21:45,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Why did so many people come tonight?</b></font>

343
00:21:45,244 --> 00:21:47,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You know they're not here to see the R32.</b></font>

344
00:21:47,944 --> 00:21:50,954
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah, they want to see that Eight-Six drift!</b></font>

345
00:21:50,954 --> 00:21:56,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They say he barrels through
corners as if they're straightaways!</b></font>

346
00:21:56,994 --> 00:21:59,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't wait to see this!</b></font>

347
00:21:59,124 --> 00:22:02,194
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh... I see...</b></font>

348
00:22:02,194 --> 00:22:08,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Uh, if he happens to show up,
could you ask him to call home?</b></font>

349
00:22:08,504 --> 00:22:10,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Thanks...</b></font>

350
00:22:13,744 --> 00:22:17,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's no use... I can't find him...</b></font>

351
00:22:17,014 --> 00:22:18,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn!</b></font>

352
00:22:18,414 --> 00:22:22,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where the hell are you?!
Give me back my Eight-Six!</b></font>

353
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

354
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>So no one intervenes</i></b></font>

355
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, I don't want to stop</i></b></font>

356
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if you cry because of a sacrificed love</i></b></font>

357
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Aim for the peak, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

358
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! The warning chime is so cheap!</i></b></font>

359
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The sheep should clear the road</i></b></font>

360
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

361
00:23:00,054 --> 00:23:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Easy motivation is total stimulation</i></b></font>

362
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You tried to escape,</i>
<i>but anywhere is a safety zone</i></b></font>

363
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:12,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something is within your grasp</i>
<i>and something is forgotten</i></b></font>

364
00:23:12,004 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Even if the world ends it will never change</i></b></font>

365
00:23:15,934 --> 00:23:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beasty shout, no one can touch you</i></b></font>

366
00:23:24,014 --> 00:23:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Cross over now to the time of an intense dream</i></b></font>

367
00:23:31,384 --> 00:23:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, split the darkness</i></b></font>

368
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like a streak to the peak</i></b></font>

369
00:23:37,394 --> 00:23:43,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Erase the freezing darkness worldwide</i></b></font>

370
00:23:43,534 --> 00:23:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, and open the road</i></b></font>

371
00:23:47,404 --> 00:23:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Di-ding down, another round never slow down</i></b></font>

372
00:23:50,074 --> 00:23:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A point 01 second knockdown</i></b></font>

373
00:23:52,074 --> 00:23:54,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Reverberations left behind,</i>
<i>disappear to the next town</i></b></font>

374
00:23:54,274 --> 00:23:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The losers are left in the dust</i></b></font>

375
00:23:56,114 --> 00:23:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Let's ignore the constraints of logic</i></b></font>

376
00:23:58,074 --> 00:24:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cause they're a pain</i></b></font>

377
00:24:00,044 --> 00:24:02,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>A streaker runs naked across the street</i></b></font>

378
00:24:02,184 --> 00:24:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something they would know</i></b></font>

379
00:24:03,384 --> 00:24:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream,</i>
<i>continue on the unending road</i></b></font>

380
00:24:07,424 --> 00:24:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't look back on your love or your past</i></b></font>

381
00:24:11,424 --> 00:24:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Go forward and you'll shine brightly</i></b></font>

382
00:24:15,494 --> 00:24:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, you're living in the now</i></b></font>

383
00:24:26,604 --> 00:24:28,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Kenji, who do you think will win</i></b></font>

384
00:24:28,514 --> 00:24:32,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>this battle Itsuki got us into,</i>
<i>the R32 or the Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

385
00:24:32,184 --> 00:24:34,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Of course, I'd like to say the Eight-Six...</i></b></font>

386
00:24:34,414 --> 00:24:38,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>...but I don't know if even Takumi</i>
<i>can beat a GT-R, the fastest domestic.</i></b></font>

387
00:24:38,284 --> 00:24:41,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>The biggest question is if</i>
<i>Takumi will even come to race!</i></b></font>

388
00:24:41,284 --> 00:24:44,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If he doesn't show up,</i>
<i>then Kenji will once more...</i></b></font>

389
00:24:44,254 --> 00:24:45,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't say it!</i></b></font>

390
00:24:45,864 --> 00:24:48,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next time on Initial D, "Time's Almost Up!"</i></b></font>

391
00:24:48,394 --> 00:24:51,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi, please get here soon!</i></b></font>

392
00:24:51,464 --> 00:24:53,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

